CONECTIVA LINUX SECURITY ANNOUNCEMENT 
- --------------------------------------------------------------------------

PACKAGE   : mplayer
SUMMARY   : Fixes for mplayer vulnerabilities
DATE      : 2005-01-05 08:59:00
ID        : CLA-2005:910
RELEVANT
RELEASES  : 9, 10

- -------------------------------------------------------------------------

DESCRIPTION
 MPlayer[1] is a multimedia player that supports several video and
 audio codecs.
 
 iDEFENSE[2] found a buffer overflow vulnerability[3] due to an error
 in dynamically allocating memory and further investigation by mplayer
 team found more vulnerabilities. This announcement fixes these
 vulnerabilities.


SOLUTION
 It is recommended that all mplayer users upgrade to the latest
 packages.
 
 
 REFERENCES
 1.http://mplayerhq.hu/
 2.http://www.idefense.com/
 3.http://www.idefense.com/application/poi/display?id=166


